answerText: The End of the Road[10] Jacob is a professor at the fictional Wicomico State Teacher's College in this state. Many of Barth's novels are set in this state, including The Sot-weed Factor, in which the poet Ebenezer Cooke is named Poet Laureate of this state by Charles Calvert, 3rd Baron Baltimore.
